text: Novokarachevo () is a rural locality (a village) in Mavlyutovsky Selsoviet, Mishkinsky District, Bashkortostan, Russia. The population was 114 as of 2010. There are 3 streets. == Geography == It is located 14 km from Mishkino, 3 km from Tatarbayevo. == References == Category:Rural localities in Mishkinsky District
title: Novokarachevo
